TY  - JOUR
TI  - Testing for Serial Correlation after Least Squares Regression
AU  - Hannan, E. J.
AU  - Terrell, R. D.
AB  - [Fourier methods are used to investigate tests for the significance of the residuals from a regression (including an autoregression). Attention is concentrated on the relevant case where the exogenous variables in the regression have spectra concentrated at the origin of frequencies.]
